<!--What Are Plastics-->
<div id="plastics" class="container pt-5">
    <section class="text-center">
        <h2 id="whatArePlastics" class="display-4" style="color: #42ABC5;">What are plastics?</h2>
        <p id="whatArePlasticsDesc" class="mt-4 mb-5 h5" style="color: rgba(9, 92, 120, 1);">It is a material widely used in our daily lives. The word “plastics” refers to the wide range of materials its made of, specifically polymers.</p>

        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 mb-4">
                <div class="card card-font-color hover-shadow" style="background-color: #71C1BA;">
                    <div class="bg-image" data-mdb-ripple-color="light">
                        <img src="/images/theyre_polymers.png" class="img-fluid" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">They're Polymers</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Polymers are either natural or synthetic substances composed of molecules linked to each other. Plastics fall in the synthetic/semi-synthetic category of polymers.<br><br><br>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 mb-4">
                <div class="card card-font-color hover-shadow" style="background-color: #71C1BA;">
                    <div class="bg-image" data-mdb-ripple-color="light">
                        <img src="~/images/pexels-mali-maeder-802221.jpg" class="img-fluid" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">They're Versatile</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Plastics has various types and has a wide range of applicaitons. It’s moldable, durable, and cheap to produce. It’s what make our lives cleaner, more convenient and enjoyable.<br><br><br>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 mb-4">
                <div class="card card-font-color hover-shadow" style="background-color: #71C1BA;">
                    <div class="bg-image" data-mdb-ripple-color="light">
                        <img src="/images/pexels-stijn-dijkstra-2583836.jpg" class="img-fluid" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">They're not all Innovative</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            As much as it improves our lives in many aspects, it is also responsible for the destruction of our environment due to its whopping life span of 500-1000 years before breaking down. Which affects marine life as well as the atmosphere due to carbon emissions amidst its life cycle.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<!--Single Use Plastics-->
<div id="singleUse" class="vh-100 bg-image mt-5">
    <div class="mask" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 146, 132, 0) 0%, #00443E 100%), linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 0%, rgba(0, 68, 62, 0.5) 100%), linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 4.69%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 67.71%);">
        <div class="container d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-center h-100">
            <div class="text-white">
                <h1 class="display-2">Single Use Plastics</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="its-everywhere" class="overflow-hidden">
    <div id="its-everywhere-container" style="width: 500vw;">
        <!--It's Everywhere 1-->
        <section id="everywhere" class="vh-100 vw-100 bg-image float-start position-relative">
            <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center text-center h-100">
                <div class="text-white">
                    <h1 class="display-2 font-weight-bold pt-5 mt-5">IT'S EVERYWHERE</h1>
                    <h1 class="h4 font-weight-light pb-5">Single use plastics are ubiquitous. From the plastic water bottles we throw away, the ketchup packets we open, to the grocery bags we use to store the things we bought. It doesn’t seem like a lot of waste considering its size and density, but what if billions of others think the same?</h1>
                    <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                            <div class="row display-1 pb-2"><p class="text-center font-weight-bold">300</p><br><p class="text-center">million</p></div>
                            <div class="row h4"><p class="text-center">Is how much metric tons of plastics are produced worldwide, annually.</p></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 mt-3">
                            <div class="row display-1 pb-2"><p class="text-center font-weight-bold">4.8</p><br><p class="text-center">million</p></div>
                            <div class="row h4"><p class="text-center">Is the minimum amount of metric tons of plastic are making its way to the ocean, annually.</p></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                            <div class="row display-1 pb-2"><p class="text-center font-weight-bold">8.3</p><br><p class="text-center">billion</p></div>
                            <div class="row h4"><p class="text-center">Is the amount of metric tons of plastic produced in total, worldwide.</p></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!--It's Everywhere 2-->
        <section id="everywhere2" class="vh-100 vw-100 bg-image float-start position-relative" style="width: calc(100% / 5);">
            <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center text-center h-100">
                <div class="text-white">
                    <h1 class="display-2 font-weight-bold pt-5 mt-5">IT'S EVERYWHERE</h1>
                    <p class="h4 font-weight-light pb-5 mb-4">Despite the sheer amount we produce each year, recycling is not enough to prevent it from reaching and polluting our environment.<br><br></p>
                    <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                            <div class="row display-1 pb-2"><p class="text-center font-weight-bold">9%</p></div>
                            <div class="row h4"><p class="text-center">Is how much plastic is being recycled a year</p></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                            <div class="row display-1 pb-2"><p class="text-center font-weight-bold">12%</p></div>
                            <div class="row h4"><p class="text-center">Is the amount of plastic that is burned annually</p></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                            <div class="row display-1 pb-2"><p class="text-center font-weight-bold">79%</p></div>
                            <div class="row h4"><p class="text-center">Is the amount of plastic that sticks around annually</p></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

